Color Scheme: Blue Gold: Berkely theme: Hibernation helper?

Permissions:
usage access (To lock the screen forest style)


Features: 

TimePicker widget to select wake up time:

when time is selected/turned on: 
have the time set and add button to "Go to Sleep"
display time remaining until then

When go to sleep Button is pressed:
record the time pressed
Lock the screen (Forest Style)
add a disrupt/wakeup button
turn alarm on

When Alarm goes off:
Wake UP button
Turn off alarm (leave it set on the same time though)
